    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Iterator<E>

    public class HashedStorageStructureIterator<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Iterator<E>
    This class implements the Iterator interface for a HashedStorageStructure. It allows the user to traverse the structure in increasing order of filtration index and dimension.
    Author:
    Andrew Tausz
